channel.title: Looking for a co owner/owner READ!
channel.description:
hey guys well i"m looking for a co owner or owner it doesn't matter. i don't care if u have 1 post or not all i need to know is if your gonna be a good co owner/owner.i"m mostly looking for a co owner/owner that can do the following,web design,coder, etc. i don't have a source/client but im very active. i"m home schooled. so i"m on most of the time. the source and client have to be either blank and then we can code or it can be a coded server with everything already in it. i don't like leeching so when we start working together were not gonna leech were gonna make a legit server coded by us. i"m a very good coder but im a good learner so if your willing to help me code then awesome. the co owner/owner will get 50% donations. when im not on the server i expect the co owner/owner to take over my job while im gone. well i guess some things i expect from this person but there's one more thing. i would like this server to be a pking server. well thanks for taking the time to read this and i hope you will put this in thought. contact information: email: campyanth@gmail.com aim: campyanth
i like to be contacted over aim. i do not have a msn yet but i will make 1 later today. note- the only reason i can't find a source/client is because i am never lucky enough to find 1.
